Package com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.reasoner.classification

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SnomedReasonerService
    Represents the RPC interface for the SNOMED CT reasoner service.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractEquivalenceSet
    Represents an abstract equivalence set, covering both concepts equivalent with another one, and unsatisfiable concepts (equivalent to owl:Nothing).
    AbstractResponse
    An abstract superclass for query responses.
    ClassificationSettings
    Carries all parameters required for starting a classification for a branch.
    EquivalenceSet
    Represents a regular equivalence set with one suggested concept as a replacement for the others.
    GetEquivalentConceptsResponse
    The return type of SnomedReasonerService#getEquivalentConcepts(UUID) requests.
    GetResultResponse
    The return type of SnomedReasonerService#getResult(UUID) requests.
    GetResultResponseChanges
    Captures a reasoner change set for review purposes.
    PersistChangesResponse
    The return type of SnomedReasonerService#persistChanges(UUID, String) requests.
    UnsatisfiableSet
    Represents unsatisfiable equivalence sets (holding concepts equivalent to owl:Nothing).
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AbstractResponse.Type
    Enumerates the possible types of a response.
